        "content": "<p>afonso360 opened <a href=\"https://github.com/bytecodealliance/wasmtime/pull/4738\">PR #4738</a> from <code>fix-inst-fmt</code> to <code>main</code>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p><span aria-label=\"wave\" class=\"emoji emoji-1f44b\" role=\"img\" title=\"wave\">:wave:</span> Hey,</p>\n<p>So in #4733 oss-fuzz discovered that we have pretty much been using the wrong instruction formats for all opcodes for a while... (Thanks @jameysharp for digging into this!).</p>\n<p>This PR does 2 things:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>Force fuzzgen to use the correct InstructionFormat for each opcode </li>\n<li>Add an assert to all InstructionFormat inserters to ensure that this does not happen again (even for other users of cranelift).</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Fixes #4733<br>\ncc: @cfallin </p>\n</blockquote>",
